The Airship is found atop [[The Beanstalk]], which is located in [[The Nearby Plains]] (once you've been able to plant an [[enchanted bean]]).

Must have 90 of main stat to enter. If your main stat isn't high enough, you will see the following message:

:You step up to the gangplank of the Airship, but before you can actually reach the ship, a gust of wind blows you backwards, and you land headfirst at the bottom of the beanstalk.

<center>(You must have at least 90 $stat to adventure here.)</center>


