==References==
*This location is a parody of the Airship from ''[[Wikipedia:Final Fantasy|The Final Fantasy series]]''; all of the encounters within refer to the ''Final Fantasy'' games (with the exception of the Irritating Series of Random Encounters, which depicts slimes from the [[wikipedia:Dragon Warrior|''Dragon Warrior'']] series, as well as the Spunky Princess, who is more of an RPG archetype than a specific reference), most notably ''[[Wikipedia:Final Fantasy VII|Final Fantasy VII]].'' The term "penultimate," which means "next to last," pokes fun at the name "Final" Fantasy.

